(2, 1, '2015-05-10 12:07:29', '2015-05-10 11:07:29', 'This is an example page. It''s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I''m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin'' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://www.declondon.com/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Sample Page', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2015-06-27 14:02:43', '2015-06-27 13:02:43', '', 0, 'http://www.declondon.com/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(4, 1, '2015-05-10 12:19:44', '2015-05-10 11:19:44', '<h1>Driving Lessons Offer</h1>\r\nIf getting the lowest price is what matters the most, then you are probably in the right place here in declondon.com. Our prices are the most competitive in North London. We have various range of courses available to suit each individuals needs. Please call us to find out more.\r\n<p class="lead">02072413322 or 07780111785</p>\r\n<p class="lead">Our <strong>cheapest driving lessons</strong> start from £18 per hour. This lessons are offered in Hackney and East London and North London areas. You won''t find cheaper driving tuition than our Special Driving Lessons Offer</p>\r\nDeclondon will arrange a Pick up from your home, train station or anywhere in London. We cover many postcodes in London.\r\n\r\nIf what you want is professional Driving Lessons in East London based driving school than declondon can help you. we are offering professional Manual and Automatic driving lessons with Fully Qualified Male and Female Driving Instructors in most East and North London areas.\r\n\r\nAll driving lessons are fun, structured and professional and we accept credit and debit card payments. if your in a hurry to get driving, why not pick our popular intensive courses where you could be driving in just 5 days!\r\n\r\nwe also offer theory test training within a classroom including Hazard Perception training to prepare you for your theory test- our theory test training', 'Driving Lessons Offer', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'special-offer', '', '', '2015-06-27 14:15:15', '2015-06-27 13:15:15', '', 0, 'http://www.declondon.com/?p=4', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(5, 1, '2015-05-10 12:18:25', '2015-05-10 11:18:25', '', 'driving-instructor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'driving-instructor', '', '', '2015-05-10 12:18:42', '2015-05-10 11:18:42', '', 4, 'http://www.declondon.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/driving-instructor.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(7, 1, '2015-05-10 12:22:27', '2015-05-10 11:22:27', '[irf_contact_form]\r\n<p class="lead">Book your driving lessons with dec driving school. If you prefer, call us on 02072413322 or 07780111785 to book a lesson</p>', 'Book Driving Lesson', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'booking-request', '', '', '2015-07-02 16:52:19', '2015-07-02 15:52:19', '', 0, 'http://www.declondon.com/?p=7', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(10, 1, '2015-05-10 12:24:14', '2015-05-10 11:24:14', '<h1>Intensive Driving Course</h1>\r\nThese intensive lessons are aimed at new and experienced drivers who want to get their full UK drivers license as quick as possible.\r\nFor detailed explanations on our intensive courses designed specifically for you, please call one of our helpful advisors and we will be happy to help you.\r\n<h2>Manual Lessons</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<table class="table table-bordered" style="width: 600px;">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Hours Of Lessons</th>\r\n<th>Price</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Single Lesson</td>\r\n<td>£20</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>5</td>\r\n<td>£98</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>10</td>\r\n<td>£190</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>20</td>\r\n<td>£370</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>30</td>\r\n<td>£540</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Automatic Driving Lessons</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<table class="table table-bordered" style="width: 600px;">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Hours Of Lessons</th>\r\n<th>Price</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>1 hour</td>\r\n<td>£23</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>5 hours</td>\r\n<td>£110</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>10 hours</td>\r\n<td>£215</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>20 hours</td>\r\n<td>£420</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Hire a car for driving test</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<table class="table table-bordered" style="width: 600px;">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Test Location</th>\r\n<th>Price</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Wood Green - Chingford - Wanstead</td>\r\n<td>£80</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Hendon - Mill Hill - Barnet - Enfield - Barking</td>\r\n<td>£90</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>Pass Plus Lessons</h4>\r\n<div>\r\n<table class="table table-bordered" style="width: 600px;">\r\n	\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Motorway Lessons, 3 hours</td>\r\n			<td>£75</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Pass - Plus Course</td>\r\n			<td>£150</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<p class="lead">if you would like us to book your theory and driving test, this will cost extra £120 which includes fast track driving test</p>\r\nOur driving lessons prices start as low as £18 an hour. We have more that 31 years of experience in teaching how to drive. This quality of tuition for this price is not easy to find anywhere else in London. When we say <strong>Cheap Driving Course in Hackney</strong>, we really mean it. You won''t find this low driving tuition anywhere.\r\nPlease call us to find out more or visit our booking page to fill in the booking form.', 'Intensive Driving Course', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'intensive-driving-course', '', '', '2015-07-08 16:32:50', '2015-07-08 15:32:50', '', 0, 'http://www.declondon.com/?p=10', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(11, 1, '2015-05-10 12:24:00', '2015-05-10 11:24:00', '', 'learn-to-drive-with-new-car', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'learn-to-drive-with-new-car', '', '', '2015-05-10 12:24:08', '2015-05-10 11:24:08', '', 10, 'http://www.declondon.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/learn-to-drive-with-new-car.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(13, 1, '2015-05-10 12:25:37', '2015-05-10 11:25:37', '<h1><span style="color: #be0319;">D</span><span style="color: #333399;">EC</span> Hackney Driving School:</h1>\r\n<h2>DEC driving school has been providing quality driving lessons since 1987. Our aim is simple, we want to deliver a high quality of service to you.</h2>\r\nCurrently DEC is training students of all ages and from all walks of life. We have patient and experienced driving instuctors across West, North West, North and East London. DEC is well established as one of the best local and most popular driving schools in these areas.\r\n\r\nDEC was awarded the outstanding achievement award year 2007 by ADI Federation for its achievements in the industry.\r\n\r\nWe are a highly recognized and known driving school. Other than teaching people to drive, we also do driving instructors training. DEC is known in the industry as a driving school which is actively involved in a variety of driving matters such as driving safety and green driving.\r\n\r\nSo, with our experience and our dynamic team of keen, friendly and professional driving instructors, there is no better driving school than us at DEC where you can learn and train.\r\n\r\nCall us to schedule an appointment today: <strong>0800 043 0505 / </strong><strong>0207 241 3322</strong>\r\n\r\nDEClondon driving school is really the most affordable way to learn how to drive in Hackney. Learning to drive in Hackney has become very expensive, and we offer driving lessons as low as £18 an hour. Do not hesitate to call to find out more. You can also fill in our <a href="http://www.declondon.com/2015/05/10/booking-request/">booking form</a>, and we will call you back as soon as possible.', 'Hackney Driving School', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hackney-driving-school', '', '\nhttp://www.declondon.com/2015/05/10/booking-request/', '2015-05-23 14:48:25', '2015-05-23 13:48:25', '', 0, 'http://www.declondon.com/?p=13', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(15, 1, '2015-05-10 12:26:50', '2015-05-10 11:26:50', '<h1><span style="color: #be0319;">D</span><span style="color: #333399;">EC</span> Driving Instructor Course</h1>\r\n<h5>We can put you on the road to a prosperous career; we can help you get fully qualified. We can provide all stationery and material, advice and back up support.</h5>\r\nBut first and foremost you need to check your eligibility to apply to become an ADI with :\r\n<ul class="tick">\r\n	<li>You need a full UK or EU car driving licence</li>\r\n	<li>You have not been disqualified from driving in the last four years</li>\r\n	<li>Required eyesight (read car number plate from 27.5 metres)</li>\r\n	<li>Be fit and proper (criminal checks)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThere are three parts to pass in the process of becoming an ADI. Once you passed part I and part II, you can start teaching real learners on trainee licence and earn money as driving instructor.\r\n\r\nDEC can help with your training and to smoothly pass all the steps towards becoming a fully qualified instructor.\r\n\r\nWe have been training ADI’s from start to finish as well as helping PDI’s from other schools for over 25 years. We have the experience and know how to help you succeed. We’ve been doing this for so long you cannot go wrong with us.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://declondon.com/index.php/become-an-instructor?page_id=9">Contact us</a> to arrange an appointment to discuss Prices and Training.\r\n\r\nYou can be assured that our course will help you set-up your own driving instructor business once you are qualified. There are not many driving courses in Hackney and East London with many years of experience as Declondon Drving School.', 'Driving Instructor Course', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'driving-instructor-course', '', '\nhttp://declondon.com/index.php/become-an-instructor?page_id=9', '2015-05-23 14:43:39', '2015-05-23 13:43:39', '', 0, 'http://www.declondon.com/?p=15', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(17, 1, '2015-05-10 12:27:40', '2015-05-10 11:27:40', '<h1>Pass Plus Lessons</h1>\r\nBecome a Better, Safer, Less Cash-Strapped Driver!\r\nOnce you have passed your test and now you want to cut your insurance premiums down to size. You’d probably like to become a more confident and self-assured driver too.\r\n\r\nIn that case, Pass Plus is for you. Pass Plus is the government’s scheme for improving the safety record of newly qualified drivers – and saving them a few quid into the bargain. In fact everyone is so keen to help you become a better driver, your local authority may well pay back almost half the cost of your Pass Plus lessons.\r\nGet Your Certificate and a Bundle of New Skills:\r\nAlthough there’s no test for a Pass Plus certificate, you do have to work hard. Pass Plus involves a minimum of six one-hour sessions covering town and out-of-town driving, all-weather and night-time driving, and driving on motorways and dual carriageways.\r\n\r\nYou come away with much more confidence, a shed-load of new skills, and a certificate that qualifies you for discounts on your insurance. Don’t delay savings and refunds are time-sensitive:\r\n\r\nThere are time limits to Pass Plus benefits. To be in with a chance of a refund or insurance savings, you must apply for Pass Plus within 12 months of passing your test. Insurance Discounts Pass Plus is all about being a safer driver, which is why most insurers are offering discounts to Pass Plus drivers.\r\nLondon Borough Refunds\r\nIf you’re aged between 17 and 25, you could get a refund of £70 on your Pass Plus fees. For details, Call Transport for London on 0845 230 1725.\r\nOther Local Authority Refunds\r\nMany local authorities are offering Pass Plus incentives. Call your local council to find out what’s happening in your area.\r\n\r\nOur Pass Plus Lessons are held in Hackney and other East London areas. Pass lessons will make you really confident driver. if you have any questions about the pass plus lessons declondon offers, please do not hesitate to contact us.', 'Pass Plus Lessons', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'pass-plus-lessons', '', '', '2015-06-27 12:01:38', '2015-06-27 11:01:38', '', 0, 'http://www.declondon.com/?p=17', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(20, 1, '2015-05-10 12:31:20', '2015-05-10 11:31:20', '<h1>Driving Lessons in Hackney</h1>\r\nDec London is a driving school in Hackney - London. We cover many areas of North London\r\nDEC Hackney Driving School: DEC driving schools has been providing quality driving lessons since 1987. Our aim is simple, we want to deliver a high quality of service to you. Currently DEC is training students of all ages and from all walks of life. We have patient and experienced driving instructors in North and East London.\r\n\r\nWe are a highly recognized and known driving school. Other than teaching people to drive, we also do driving instructors training. DEC is known in the industry as a driving school which is actively involved in a variety of driving matters such as driving safety and green driving.', 'Driving Lessons in Hackney', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'home', '', '', '2015-05-23 14:24:23', '2015-05-23 13:24:23', '', 0, 'http://www.declondon.com/?page_id=20', 0, 'page', '', 0),
