(171, 1, '2015-06-27 14:02:43', '2015-06-27 13:02:43', 'This is an example page. It''s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I''m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin'' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://www.declondon.com/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Sample Page', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-27 14:02:43', '2015-06-27 13:02:43', '', 2, 'http://www.declondon.com/2015/06/27/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(172, 1, '2015-06-27 14:15:15', '2015-06-27 13:15:15', '<h1>Driving Lessons Offer</h1>\r\nIf getting the lowest price is what matters the most, then you are probably in the right place here in declondon.com. Our prices are the most competitive in North London. We have various range of courses available to suit each individuals needs. Please call us to find out more.\r\n<p class="lead">02072413322 or 07780111785</p>\r\n<p class="lead">Our <strong>cheapest driving lessons</strong> start from £18 per hour. This lessons are offered in Hackney and East London and North London areas. You won''t find cheaper driving tuition than our Special Driving Lessons Offer</p>\r\nDeclondon will arrange a Pick up from your home, train station or anywhere in London. We cover many postcodes in London.\r\n\r\nIf what you want is professional Driving Lessons in East London based driving school than declondon can help you. we are offering professional Manual and Automatic driving lessons with Fully Qualified Male and Female Driving Instructors in most East and North London areas.\r\n\r\nAll driving lessons are fun, structured and professional and we accept credit and debit card payments. if your in a hurry to get driving, why not pick our popular intensive courses where you could be driving in just 5 days!\r\n\r\nwe also offer theory test training within a classroom including Hazard Perception training to prepare you for your theory test- our theory test training', 'Driving Lessons Offer', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-27 14:15:15', '2015-06-27 13:15:15', '', 4, 'http://www.declondon.com/2015/06/27/4-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
