rs</span>of professional training combined with<span style="color: #339966;">22 hours</span>of private practice. Learners who prepare this way, with a combination of plenty of professional training and plenty of practice, do better in the test.<a href="http://www.direct.gov.uk/en/Motoring/LearnerAndNewDrivers/PracticalTest/DG_4022483">read more.</a>', 'Price List', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '26-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-03 17:57:41', '2015-07-03 16:57:41', '', 26, 'http://www.declondon.com/2015/07/03/26-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
